cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.NI, cs.HC, cs.SI

The paper focuses on security and privacy issues in smart home devices, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of IoT Inspector to collect labeled network traffic also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). The potential applications of the dataset in healthcare (cs.HC) and network management (cs.SI) also suggest these categories as likely possibilities.
